      "ja": "たぶん今回",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll run from the light",
      "zh": "我會逃離光明",
      "ja": "僕は光から逃げるだろう",
      "time": "00:01:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I trace your silhouette",
      "zh": "我描繪你的輪廓",
      "ja": "君のシルエットをなぞる",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Under neon signs",
