      "time": "00:04:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I won't break the soul",
      "zh": "我不會讓靈魂破碎",
      "ja": "僕は魂を壊さない",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And you'll be carried out",
      "zh": "而你會被帶走",
      "ja": "そして君は運ばれるだろう",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Learning that trust",
      "zh": "學會信任",
      "ja": "信頼を学ぶ",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That delicate hearts can love",
      "zh": "脆弱的心也能去愛",
      "ja": "繊細な心も愛せることを",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Without turning to dust",
      "zh": "而不會化為塵埃",
      "ja": "塵にならずに",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Too delicate",
      "zh": "太脆弱了",
      "ja": "あまりにも繊細だ",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But in your arms",
      "zh": "但在你的懷抱中",
      "ja": "でも君の腕の中で",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm starting to see",
      "zh": "我開始看到",
      "ja": "僕は見始めている",
      "time": "00:04:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe fragile and brave",
      "zh": "也許脆弱與勇敢",
      "ja": "繊細さと勇敢さが",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can both live in me",
      "zh": "都能同時存在於我",
      "ja": "僕の中に共存できる",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Too delicate",
      "zh": "太脆弱了",
      "ja": "あまりにも繊細だ",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't let me go",
      "zh": "不要放開我",
      "ja": "僕を離さないで",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ohh",
      "zh": "喔",
      "ja": "ああ",
      "time": "00:04:45"
    }
  ]
}